Subject: Welcome to Dryad!

Thank you for registering for an account at datadryad.org. Dryad is a open-access, non-profit, curated repository for research data underlying publications. 

To complete your registration, please click the link below:

 {0}

DID YOU KNOW? 
- We partner with journals to make data archiving easy. Many journals cover the Dryad data publishing fee: http://datadryad.org/pages/journalLookup
- More about the Dryad organization and mission: https://datadryad.org/pages/organization
- Stay informed of the latest news:
http://blog.datadryad.org/
http://twitter.com/datadryad

Dryad respects the privacy of our users and works to protect the personally identifiable information we collect, which is limited to name and contact information. View our privacy policy: https://datadryad.org/pages/policies#privacy

If you need assistance, please email help@datadryad.org. For more information about using or submitting data, please see http://datadryad.org/pages/faq.

Best regards,

The Dryad Team
